OL,3,CBid to create AI Authority amid pleas
OL,4,Cfor swifter action from UK Government
OL,6,FBritain risks "sliding into global
OL,7,Firrelevance" on artificial
OL,8,Fintelligence (AI) if the Government
OL,9,Fdoes not introduce new laws to
OL,10,Fregulate the sector, according to a
OL,11,FConservative peer.
OL,13,FA new body, known as the AI Authority,
OL,14,Fwould be established under a proposal
OL,15,Ftabled in Parliament by Lord Holmes of
OL,16,FRichmond.
