OL,3,CBid to create AI Authority amid pleas
OL,4,Cfor swifter action from UK Government
OL,6,FHis Artificial Intelligence
OL,7,F(Regulation) Bill, to be debated at
OL,8,Fsecond reading on Friday, would
OL,9,Frequire the authority to push forward
OL,10,FAI regulation in the UK and assess and
OL,11,Fmonitor potential risks to the economy.
OL,13,FSecurity, fairness, accountability and
OL,14,Ftransparency are among the principles
OL,15,Fthat the AI Authority must take into
OL,16,Fconsideration, according to the Bill.
OL,18,FThe Government believes a non-
OL,19,Fstatutory approach provides "critical
OL,20,Fadaptability" but has pledged to keep
OL,21,Fit under review.
