OL,3,CBid to create AI Authority amid pleas
OL,4,Cfor swifter action from UK Government
OL,6,FLord Holmes said: "The current
OL,7,FGovernment approach risks the UK
OL,8,Fsliding into global irrelevance on
OL,9,Fthis hugely important issue of
OL,10,Fprotecting citizen rights and ensuring
OL,11,FAI is developed and deployed in a
OL,12,Fhumanity-enhancing, rather than a
OL,13,Fsociety-destroying, way.
OL,15,F"The Government claims that their
OL,16,Flight-touch approach is 'pro-
OL,17,Finnovation' but innovation is not
OL,18,Faided by uncertainty and instability.
OL,26,@nD@SOUwD@AOU
