OL,3,CBid to create AI Authority amid pleas
OL,4,Cfor swifter action from UK Government
OL,6,F"AI offers some of the greatest
OL,7,Fopportunities for our economy, our
OL,8,Fsociety, our human selves.
OL,10,F"It also, if unregulated holds obvious
OL,11,Fexistential harms. Self-governance and
OL,12,Fvoluntary agreements just don't cut it.
OL,14,F"We need leadership, right-sized
OL,15,Fregulation, right now.
OL,17,F"The UK can, the UK must lead when it
OL,18,Fcomes to ethical AI.
OL,20,F"This Bill offers them that very
OL,21,Fopportunity. I hope they take it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUyD@AOU|D@AOU}D@bO]
