OL,3,CBid to create AI Authority amid pleas
OL,4,Cfor swifter action from UK Government
OL,6,FThe Bill would also seek to ensure any
OL,7,Fperson involved in training AI would
OL,8,Fhave to supply to the authority a
OL,9,Frecord of all third-party data and
OL,10,Fintellectual property (IP) they used
OL,11,Fand offer assurances that informed
OL,12,Fconsent was secured for its use.
OL,14,FLord Holmes added on the labelling
OL,15,Fsystem: "People would know if a
OL,16,Fservice or a good had used or deployed
OL,17,FAI in the provision of that service."
