OL,3,CBid to create AI Authority amid pleas
OL,4,Cfor swifter action from UK Government
OL,6,FSpeaking in November last year, Rishi
OL,7,FSunak said Britain's AI safety summit
OL,8,Fwould "tip the balance in favour of
OL,9,Fhumanity" after reaching an agreement
OL,10,Fwith technology firms to vet their
OL,11,Fmodels before their release.
OL,13,FThe Prime Minister said "binding
OL,14,Frequirements" would likely to be
OL,15,Fneeded to regulate the technology, but
OL,16,Fnow is the time to move quickly
OL,17,Fwithout laws.
OL,19,FElon Musk, the owner of social media
OL,20,Fplatform X, described AI as "one of
OL,21,Fthe biggest threats" facing humanity.
