OL,3,CBid to create AI Authority amid pleas
OL,4,Cfor swifter action from UK Government
OL,6,FThe Government announced in February
OL,7,Fthat more than #100 million will be
OL,8,Fspent preparing the UK to regulate AI
OL,9,Fand use the technology safely,
OL,10,Fincluding helping to prepare and
OL,11,Fupskill regulators across different
OL,12,Fsectors.
OL,14,FMinister have chosen to use existing
OL,15,Fregulators to take on the role of
OL,16,Fmonitoring AI use within their own
OL,17,Fsectors rather than creating a new,
OL,18,Fcentral regulator dedicated to the
OL,19,Femerging technology.
